#### Pivot Table

[Documentation here.](https://pandas.pydata.org/pandas-docs/stable/reshaping.html#reshaping-and-pivot-tables)

```python
titanic.pivot_table(index='sex', columns='class',
                    aggfunc={'survived':sum, 'fare':'mean'})
```

